column1: Employment status (a) by labour force region, Queensland, 1999–00 to 2018–19 (b)(c)(d)
Note: The labour force statistics are on a sample basis and will include a sampling error. Caution should be used when making inferences from these estimates.
(a) Based on persons aged 15 years and over.
(c) Data have been rounded to the nearest 100 persons.
(d) The Australian Bureau of Statistics introduced new Labour Force Regions based on SA4s in January 2014 and backcast data to October 1998. As such a longer time series is not available.
Source: ABS 6291.0.55.001, Labour Force, Australia, Detailed
